that happens.

00:03:03.300 --> 00:03:08.370 align:middle line:84%
And someone can have an
experience of themselves

00:03:08.370 --> 00:03:13.930 align:middle line:84%
as, let's say something
larger than that negative self

00:03:13.930 --> 00:03:14.730 align:middle line:90%
narrative.

00:03:14.730 --> 00:03:19.770 align:middle line:84%
That ability to alter
someone's state of awareness

00:03:19.770 --> 00:03:24.420 align:middle line:84%
is a really special
property of the medicine.

00:03:24.420 --> 00:03:27.570 align:middle line:84%
>> Ketamine can be administered
by a trained medical

00:03:27.570 --> 00:03:32.610 align:middle line:84%
professional in a number of
ways, including IV infusion,

00:03:32.610 --> 00:03:36.180 align:middle line:90%
intramuscularly, and orally.

00:03:36.180 --> 00:03:38.430 align:middle line:84%
Patients can receive
treatment in a range

00:03:38.430 --> 00:03:41.760 align:middle line:84%
of different settings, from
